53
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:14,840
Shaofei.

54
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,680
Let's

55
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,480
cheers.

56
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,480
To our victory.

57
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:37,400
Shaofei.

58
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,880
I feel a bit stifled.

59
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,280
Wanna go out for a walk.

60
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,680
Song.

61
