hoping you'd finally leave that jerk.

68
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,680
I really like you.

69
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,960
You let me down greatly.

70
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,120
Song.

71
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,480
You shouldn't have betrayed me.

72
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,480
Mr. Xue, what happened?

73
00:06:58,400 --> 00:06:59,160
Injured?

74
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,880
Are you alright?

75
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,280
I'm fine.

76
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,520
Where is Yiyi?

77
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:10,200
That day Miss Song went to the warehouse

78
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,040
and saw Meng Shaofei snatched her bag.

79
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:14,480
She then suspected
Meng Shaofei killed her mom,

80
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,800
asking for my help.

81
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:21,880
Song.

82
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:23,080
Shaofei.

83
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,680
You even let her

84
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,560
do such risky things?

85
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:39,600
Calm down.

86
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,400
Mr. Xue.

87
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,280
Miss Song found something.

88
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,680
Six years ago,
Meng Shaofei never skipped class.

89
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,960
He found an Asian doppelgänger

90
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,520
to attend classes in his place.

91
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,200
She also found out

92
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,480
Meng Shaofei has two passports.

93
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,360
He returned to China

94
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,680
earlier than we expected.

95
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,840
It was before Dr. Song's death.

96
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,360
We were all misled.

97
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:02,640
It's Miss Song.

98
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:06,600
Yiyi.

99
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,840
Brother, it's me.

100
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:14,760
Where is Yiyi?

101
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,640
If you want to see her,

102
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:20,480
come to the company's rooftop alone.

103
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,640
You're awake?

104
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:42,480
Calm.

105
00:08:43,680 --> 00:08:45,160
Xue Fanyu

106
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,760
is about to be finished soon.

107
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,320
Why are you laughing?

108
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:12,280
You used Yang Nana as a front,

109
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,920
Wu Di as a shield,

110
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,800
and then me to control Xue Fanyu.

111
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:23,880
You've always hidden behind women.

112
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,120
Now,

113
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:31,400
the rat's finally come out
into the open.

114
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,840
You actually think that of me?

115
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:38,720
When did you start suspecting me?

116
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,760
Your mom's diary.

117
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,320
At first,

118
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:48,440
I just felt your particular attention
to my mom's stuff.

119
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,200
Song.

120
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,520
Shaofei.

121
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,040
Why are you here?

122
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:55,640
I finished the work.

123
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,080
Came to keep you company.

124
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,600
I'm here to pick something up.

125
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,760
I'll accompany you.

126
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:01,000
Later on,

127
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,800
I found you're not what I thought.

128
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,440
So I started to investigate you.

129
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,440
You've already got the company.

130
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,560
I just have one question.

131
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:28,840
Did you

132
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,040
kill my mom?

133
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:41,480
You'll know the answer soon.

134
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:03,160
Don't be scared.

135
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:05,440
I'll take you away.

136
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:14,960
Brother.

137
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:18,480
I've been waiting for you for ages.

138
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:30,880
Get up.

139
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,120
Turn around.

140
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:53,720
Back off.

141
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,160
Hurry up.

142
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:06,680
I said hurry up!

143
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,920
I've given you the Yulin Group.

144
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:18,280
What else do you want?

145
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:22,440
I

146
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:25,360
want your life.

147
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,560
Leave here.

148
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,240
Quiet.

149
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:30,960
What should I do?

150
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:40,160
Your suicide note is ready.

151
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:44,640
Will it be that Song died by accident?

152
00:12:45,680 --> 00:12:47,640
Or you

153
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:50,000
committed suicide out of guilt

154
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,240
for killing Dr. Song?

155
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:56,720
Fanyu, leave here!

156
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:58,040
Be quiet!

157
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:58,920
Ok, fine.

158
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,360
I'll do it.

159
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,080
Then hurry up.

160
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:45,120
If you dare to hurt her,

161
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,720
I'll never forgive you, even in death.

162
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,280
Xue Fanyu.

163
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:20,280
Go to hell.

164
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:26,280
Six years ago, that night,
it was you, right?

165
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,920
So what if it was?

166
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:29,520
After tonight, no one will know.

167
00:14:41,640 --> 00:14:42,680
