178
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:40,480
(Property Ownership; Divorce Agreement)
and the villa.

179
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,880
What's that supposed to mean?

180
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:46,800
Also this.

181
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:08,680
Mr. Xue is very sorry

182
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:10,680
for making you suffer all this.

183
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:13,200
No matter what you say,

184
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,800
he cannot forgive himself.

185
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,160
So, Mr. Xue says

186
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,120
