187
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,200
I'm sorry, Miss Song.

188
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:18,160
(The flowers have been watered.)

189
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:20,400
(Mr. Xue has been here?)

190
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,120
Xue...

191
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:24,960
Miss Song.

192
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,320
What's the matter?

193
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:34,240
Meng Shaofei admitted guilt
at the station.

194
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:35,360
One more thing.

195
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:38,280
We were all wrong about the truth

196
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:39,520
six years ago.

